                    android:textAlignment="center"
                    android:textSize="18dp" />

                <com.example.discrollview.MyTextView
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_weight="4"
                    android:padding="8dp"
                    android:text="1) Team Size - 4 members in a team  (Lone Wolves are welcome too. We might team you up during the Hackathon) Inter-College Teams are allowed \n \n
2) Originality of Code - We all start coding at the same time. This is done to keep things fair. No one is allowed to come in and build on top of previous projects.  Due credits shall be given in case some boilerplate or open source code is used. \n \n
3) Equipment - Participants have to bring their own laptops. Extension Cords, LAN Cables for fast Internet access as well as Wifi connection will be provided. \n \n
4) Decision of organizers is final and binding.
